{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Here, we propose a dialogue-based collaborative interior design task as a testbed.",
    "In this task, the goal is to discuss how to design the room interiors.",
    "Interior design tasks can be broad and may involve complex components (e.g., color palette, furniture, accessories) as well as a series of steps to be followed.",
    "To narrow down the scope of our task, we focus on furnishing a room with a chair (building upon work on richly-annotated 3D object datasets like ShapeNet (Chang et al., 2015) and ShapeGlot (Achlioptas et al., 2019); Appendix E).",
    "In this task, a human and an AI are provided with a room layout and asked to collaboratively come up with a chair design to be placed in the room through text-based dialogue."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To narrow down the scope of our task, we focus on furnishing a room with a chair (building upon work on richly-annotated 3D object datasets like ShapeNet (Chang et al., 2015) and ShapeGlot (Achlioptas et al., 2019); Appendix E)."
